au.edu.uts.eng.remotelabs.rigclient.util
Class ResourcePropertiesDescriptions

java.lang.Object
  au.edu.uts.eng.remotelabs.rigclient.util.ResourcePropertiesDescriptions
All Implemented Interfaces:
IConfigDescriptions
public class ResourcePropertiesDescriptions
extends java.lang.Object
implements IConfigDescriptions

Loads descriptions of the rig client configuration properties. The format of this file is given by the following DTD:

 <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8">
 <DOCTYPE config[
  <!ELEMENT config(property*)>
  <!ELEMENT property (#PCDATA)>
  <!ATTLIST property name stanza mandatory type format default restart example #PCDATA #REQUIRED>
 ]>

The type attribute should have one of the following types:
  • STRING
  • INTEGER
  • FLOAT
  • BOOLEAN
  • CHAR
The default location of the configuration descriptions file is 'META-INF/config-descriptions.xml' which is within the Rig Client JAR file. This may be overridden with the system property 'prop.descriptions'.
